  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the list of known songs, see <a href=\"/index.php/Songs\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Songs\">Songs</a>.</div>\n<p><b>Song</b> may refer to:\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Places\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Miscellaneous\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Miscellaneous</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Song&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Steelsong\" title=\"Aemon Steelsong\">Aemon Steelsong</a>, the son of Mance Rayder and Dalla</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dareon\" title=\"Dareon\">Dareon</a>, also known as the <i>Black singer</i></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>, who refer to themselves as <i>those who sing the song of the earth</i></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places\">Places</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Song&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>, the seat of House Caron</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Singing_Stones\" title=\"Singing Stones\">Singing Stones</a>, a group of islands in the Summer Islands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Singing_Towers\" title=\"Singing Towers\">Singing Towers</a>, towers of Nightsong</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Miscellaneous\">Miscellaneous</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Song&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Miscellaneous\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Moonsingers\" title=\"Moonsingers\">Moonsingers</a>, priestesses of the Jogos Nhai</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Sea_Song\" title=\"Sea Song\">Sea Song</a></i>, the longship of Lord Rodrik Harlaw</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Singer%27s_stew\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Singer&#39;s stew\">Singer's stew</a>, a term coined by Tyrion Lannister</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Singing_squid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Singing squid\">Singing squid</a>, a species of mollusc</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Song_of_the_Sea:_How_the_Lands_Were_Severed\" title=\"Song of the Sea: How the Lands Were Severed\">Song of the Sea: How the Lands Were Severed</a></i>, a book written by Archmaester Cassander</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Songbird\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Songbird\">Songbird</a>, a species of bird</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Songs_the_Drowned_Men_Sing\" title=\"Songs the Drowned Men Sing\">Songs the Drowned Men Sing</a></i>, a book written by Maester Kirth</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Song_of_the_Rhoyne\" title=\"The Song of the Rhoyne\">The Song of the Rhoyne</a>, a play</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_song_of_ice_and_fire\" title=\"The song of ice and fire\">The song of ice and fire</a>, a prophecy</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Song&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Campaign_Guide\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide\">A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire:_Tactics\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics\">A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Art_of_George_R._R._Martin%27s_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Art of George R. R. Martin&#39;s A Song of Ice and Fire\">The Art of George R. R. Martin's A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405145158\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.044 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 23/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 67/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 356/2097152 bytes\nTemplate 